{"tid":1790970,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"通訊局向無綫發出強烈勸諭，指無綫未播足政府宣傳片","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T16:17:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f562369c1a0499b09646111dd6624643026fe7d8","tid":1790970,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"通訊事務管理局裁定，無綫電視在7月13日至11月26日，未有按照免費電視牌照條款，播放部分政府宣傳片，須在未來三個月額外補播，並向無綫發出強烈勸諭。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局引述無綫表示，由於新聞台需要騰出時段，播放與近日社會事件有關的突發新聞和現場直播，因此臨時取消播放部分原定的政府宣傳短片及通訊局宣傳材料，亦沒有作出補償。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局認為，現行機制已給予彈性，播放上的困難並非無法克服，又敦促無綫嚴格遵守牌照條件。按牌照規定，無綫須在各頻道按政府編製的時間表，每小時播放最多一分鐘的政府宣傳短片，及每星期播放最多五分鐘的通訊局宣傳材料。"},{"pid":"1dbc39d709fbb581f4fa469281e65b5608481269","tid":1790970,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1dbee3c0cf6febdedad64a3700c59feee040be","tid":1790970,"uid":209226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"【騎劫政府廣告2.0】停止警暴 回歸理性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n播呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cb1d8da5e264db0e4fca21693b502182b2568a","tid":1790970,"